sequenceDiagram
    participant U as 👤 User (Slack)
    participant AI as 🤖 AI Security Analyst
    participant MCP as 🔌 MCP Server
    participant LS as 🏗️ LocalStack
    U->>AI: @Shield scan environment
    AI->>MCP: scan_environment
    MCP->>LS: ListBuckets, ListUsers, ...
    LS-->>MCP: Resource snapshots
    MCP-->>AI: Scan result (15 findings)
    AI-->>U: 📊 Report: 3 Critical, 5 High, ...
    U->>AI: @Shield explain finding 1
    AI-->>U: 📝 Detailed explanation
    U->>AI: @Shield fix finding 1
    AI->>MCP: generate_terraform_fix
    MCP-->>AI: Terraform HCL code
    AI-->>U: 🏗️ Terraform block + ⚠️ Request approval
    U->>AI: @Shield approve
    AI->>MCP: execute_remediation
    MCP->>LS: put-public-access-block
    LS-->>MCP: Success
    MCP-->>AI: ✅ Remediation applied
    AI-->>U: ✅ Fix complete. Score improved!
